Class MummyBlock

java.lang.Object
com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.entity.block.Entity
com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.entity.block.enemy.MummyBlock
public class MummyBlock extends Entity
Represents a block associated with a Mummy enemy in the game.

This class extends the Entity class to include additional behavior and properties specific to Mummy enemies, such as their movement range.
